00:34:54.520 --> 00:34:56.300
And you just keep
repeating this one.

00:34:56.300 --> 00:35:00.650
So once you have this
and you have the--

00:35:00.650 --> 00:35:04.300
you just fill in the
table in the ZEMAX.

00:35:04.300 --> 00:35:06.730
And there are also other
