object information.

00:35:16.880 --> 00:35:19.390
So if your object is
in finite distance,

00:35:19.390 --> 00:35:25.240
then field means object
height or size of your object,

00:35:25.240 --> 00:35:30.400
or if it is infinite, you
can set the incident angle

00:35:30.400 --> 00:35:32.921
to the system, just
like the telescope.

